            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash and shred your<strong> lettuce </strong>finely, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Trim, then finely slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p><p>Strip your <strong>mint</strong> <strong>leaves</strong> from their stems, then chop them finely and discard the stems</p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
