            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> chopped mint</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>coriander</strong> and <strong>sliced spring onion </strong>to the <strong>cooked brown rice</strong> with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your <strong>herby rice</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>remaining rice vinegar</strong> with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and<strong> pepper </strong>– this is your<strong> dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
